'''''Chronicle of the Years of Fire''''' ( Arabic    ; French   ; aya mazina yombi asobanura "Chronicle of the Year of Embers ") ni filime yamateka yikinamico yo muri Alijeriya yakinwe muri 1975 iyobowe na Mohammed Lakhdar-Hamina . Irerekana Intambara yo kwigenga ya Alijeriya nkuko bigaragara mumaso y'umuhanzi.

Filime yatsindiye igihembo cya ''Palme d'Or'' mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes 1975 .  Yatoranijwe kandi nk'iyinjira muri Alijeriya muri Filime Nziza y'indimi z'amahanga mu bihembo bya 48 bya Academy, ariko ntiyakirwa nk'umukandida. <ref>Margaret Herrick Library, Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences</ref>

